    "title": {
      "rendered": "16 Online Job Boards for Nonprofit Professionals Worldwide"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26032\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></p>\n<p><em>The bad news?</em> Tens of millions are out of work worldwide due to the COVID-19 crisis. <em>The good news?</em> The economy will eventually bounce back and a record number of new employment opportunities will be available and many of these future jobs will be remote. Nonprofits that embrace the flexible work movement <a href=\"https://www.zippia.com/employer/8-benefits-allowing-employees-work-remotely/\"><strong>experience many benefits</strong></a>, such as increased productivity and retention and decreased expenses and pollution contribution. Win-win. Bookmark your browsers! Your next dream job is coming soon.</p>\n<h2>1) Work for Good :: <a href=\"https://www.workforgood.org/\">workforgood.org</a></h2>\n<p>Since our founding in 1999 as Opportunity Knocks, one of the first job boards focused exclusively on the mission-driven careers, our team at Work for Good has helped more than 30,000 purpose-driven organizations find the talent they need.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.workforgood.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26003\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Work-For-Good.jpg?resize=960%2C635\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"635\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Work-For-Good.jpg?w=1198&amp;ssl=1 1198w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Work-For-Good.jpg?resize=300%2C199&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Work-For-Good.jpg?resize=1024%2C678&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Work-For-Good.jpg?resize=768%2C508&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>2) United Nations Jobs (Worldwide) :: <a href=\"http://www.unjobs.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">unjobs.org</a></h2>\n<p>A comprehensive aggregator of job openings at United Nations offices worldwide.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://unjobs.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26006\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/UNJOBS.jpg?resize=960%2C618\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"618\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/UNJOBS.jpg?w=1211&amp;ssl=1 1211w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/UNJOBS.jpg?resize=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/UNJOBS.jpg?resize=1024%2C659&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/UNJOBS.jpg?resize=768%2C494&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">3) Third Sector Jobs (UK) :: <a href=\"http://jobs.thirdsector.co.uk/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">jobs.thirdsector.co.uk</a></h2>\n<p>Third Sector Jobs is a leading job site for hundreds of the latest charity jobs, voluntary jobs, and fundraising jobs in the United Kingdom.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://jobs.thirdsector.co.uk/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26008\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Third-Sector-Jobs.jpg?resize=960%2C586\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"586\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Third-Sector-Jobs.jpg?w=1157&amp;ssl=1 1157w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Third-Sector-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C183&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Third-Sector-Jobs.jpg?resize=1024%2C625&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Third-Sector-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C469&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">4) Pro Bono Australia :: <a href=\"https://probonoaustralia.com.au/jobs/\">probonoaustralia.com.au/jobs</a></h2>\n<p>Pro Bono Australia provide news, jobs and resources for the common good.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://probonoaustralia.com.au/jobs/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26009\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pro-Bono-Australia.jpg?resize=960%2C575\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"575\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pro-Bono-Australia.jpg?w=1192&amp;ssl=1 1192w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pro-Bono-Australia.jpg?resize=300%2C180&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pro-Bono-Australia.jpg?resize=1024%2C613&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Pro-Bono-Australia.jpg?resize=768%2C460&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">5) Philanthropy News Digest (US) :: <a href=\"http://philanthropynewsdigest.org/jobs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">philanthropynewsdigest.org/jobs</a></h2>\n<p>PND&#8217;s job board provides listings of current full-time job openings at\u00a0tax-exempt organizations.\u00a0Tax-exempt organizations may submit up to ten postings a month,\u00a0free of\u00a0charge.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://philanthropynewsdigest.org/jobs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26011\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PND-Jobs.jpg?resize=960%2C569\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PND-Jobs.jpg?w=1196&amp;ssl=1 1196w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PND-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PND-Jobs.jpg?resize=1024%2C607&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PND-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C455&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>6) NTEN Job Board (US) :: <a href=\"https://www.nten.org/jobs/\">nten.org/jobs</a></h2>\n<p>NTEN posts full-time nonprofit tech jobs and short-term opportunities at organizations working for social change.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nten.org/jobs/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26014\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NTEN-Jobs.jpg?resize=960%2C622\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NTEN-Jobs.jpg?w=1177&amp;ssl=1 1177w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NTEN-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NTEN-Jobs.jpg?resize=1024%2C663&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/NTEN-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C497&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>7) Nonprofit Career Network (US) :: <a href=\"https://www.nonprofitcareer.com/\">nonprofitcareer.com</a></h2>\n<p>For people who want to participate in the nonprofit or Impact Business sector and the organizations that have a need for those people.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nonprofitcareer.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26016\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nonprofit-Career-Network.jpg?resize=960%2C627\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"627\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nonprofit-Career-Network.jpg?w=1259&amp;ssl=1 1259w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nonprofit-Career-Network.jpg?resize=300%2C196&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nonprofit-Career-Network.jpg?resize=1024%2C669&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nonprofit-Career-Network.jpg?resize=768%2C501&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>8) National Council of Nonprofits (US) :: <a href=\"https://careers.councilofnonprofits.org/\">careers.councilofnonprofits.org</a></h2>\n<p>Founded in 1990, the National Council of Nonprofits is a trusted resource and advocate for America\u2019s charitable nonprofits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://careers.councilofnonprofits.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26019\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/National-Jobs.jpg?resize=960%2C676\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"676\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/National-Jobs.jpg?w=1059&amp;ssl=1 1059w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/National-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C211&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/National-Jobs.jpg?resize=1024%2C721&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/National-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C541&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">9) Idealist (Worldwide) :: <a href=\"http://www.idealist.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">idealist.org</a></h2>\n<p>Idealist connect Idealists\u2014people who want to do good\u2014with employment and volunteer opportunities for action all over the world. The website is available in <strong><a href=\"https://www.idealist.org/\">English</a></strong>, <a href=\"https://www.idealist.org/pt\"><strong>Portuguese,</strong></a> and <a href=\"https://www.idealist.org/es\"><strong>Spanish</strong></a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.idealist.org/en\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26021\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Idealist-Jobs.jpg?resize=960%2C539\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"539\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Idealist-Jobs.jpg?w=1245&amp;ssl=1 1245w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Idealist-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Idealist-Jobs.jpg?resize=1024%2C575&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Idealist-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C431&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>10) Foundation List (US) :: <a href=\"https://www.foundationlist.org/\">foundationlist.org</a></h2>\n<p>Positions actively posted and recruited for on Foundation List include part-time and full-time positions from executive to entry level.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.foundationlist.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26024\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Foundation-List.jpg?resize=960%2C577\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"577\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Foundation-List.jpg?w=1287&amp;ssl=1 1287w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Foundation-List.jpg?resize=300%2C180&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Foundation-List.jpg?resize=1024%2C616&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Foundation-List.jpg?resize=768%2C462&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">11) DevNetJobs.org (Worldwide) :: <a href=\"http://www.devnetjobs.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">devnetjobs.org</a></h2>\n<p>DevNetJobs.org agreegates international development jobs and consulting opportunities worldwide.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.devnetjobs.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26027\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DevNetJobs.jpg?resize=943%2C628\" alt=\"\" width=\"943\" height=\"628\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DevNetJobs.jpg?w=943&amp;ssl=1 943w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DevNetJobs.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DevNetJobs.jpg?resize=768%2C511&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 943px) 100vw, 943px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>12) Devex (Worldwide) :: <a href=\"https://www.devex.com/jobs\">devex.com/jobs</a></h2>\n<p>Devex is the media platform and jobs board for the global development community.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26029\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Devex-Jobs.jpg?resize=960%2C564\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Devex-Jobs.jpg?w=1203&amp;ssl=1 1203w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Devex-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Devex-Jobs.jpg?resize=1024%2C602&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Devex-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C451&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">13) Chronicle of Philanthropy (US) :: <a href=\"https://jobs.philanthropy.com/\">jobs.philanthropy.com</a></h2>\n<p>A extensive job board and career resource center for nonprofit professionals and foundation executives.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://jobs.philanthropy.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26034\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chronicle-of-Philanthropy.jpg?resize=960%2C620\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"620\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chronicle-of-Philanthropy.jpg?w=1128&amp;ssl=1 1128w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chronicle-of-Philanthropy.jpg?resize=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chronicle-of-Philanthropy.jpg?resize=1024%2C662&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Chronicle-of-Philanthropy.jpg?resize=768%2C496&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">14) Charity Village (Canada) :: <a href=\"https://charityvillage.com/search/#results/5e908bdcc752fbe89d083394?cv_volunteer_pos=exclude&amp;page_num=1&amp;kw=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">charityvillage.com</a></h2>\n<p>For more than 20 years, CharityVillage has helped thousands of Canadian charities find exceptional talent.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://charityvillage.com/search/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-26035 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Village.jpg?resize=960%2C695\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"695\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Village.jpg?w=1094&amp;ssl=1 1094w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Village.jpg?resize=300%2C217&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Village.jpg?resize=1024%2C741&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Village.jpg?resize=768%2C556&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>15) Charity Digital Jobs (UK) :: <a href=\"https://charitydigitaljobs.org/\">charitydigitaljobs.org</a></h2>\n<p>Charity Digital Jobs connects UK charities with the best digital talent in the UK.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://charitydigitaljobs.org/jobs/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26037\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Digital-Jobs.jpg?resize=960%2C691\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"691\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Digital-Jobs.jpg?w=1134&amp;ssl=1 1134w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Digital-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Digital-Jobs.jpg?resize=1024%2C737&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Charity-Digital-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C553&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">16) Bridgespan Group (US) :: <a href=\"https://www.bridgespan.org/jobs/nonprofit-jobs/nonprofit-job-board\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">bridgespan.org/jobs</a></h2>\n<p>The Bridgespan Group is a leading social impact consultancy for nonprofits and NGOs, philanthropists, and investors that also offers an online job board.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-26039\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bridgespan-Group.jpg?resize=960%2C785\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bridgespan-Group.jpg?w=997&amp;ssl=1 997w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bridgespan-Group.jpg?resize=300%2C245&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bridgespan-Group.jpg?resize=768%2C628&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color: #c30437;\"><a style=\"color: #c30437;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\"><em><strong>101 Best Practices for Nonprofits</strong></em></a></span> is a year-long blog and webinar series (written and presented by <span style=\"color: #c30437;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #c30437;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a></strong></span>) on website design, email marketing, online fundraising, and social media best practices for nonprofits, NGOs, and charities worldwide. Sign up for\u00a0<a href=\"https://mailchi.mp/nptechforgood/news\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c30437;\">Nonprofit Tech for Good\u2019s email newsletter</span></strong></a>\u00a0to be alerted of new posts.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-25066\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n",
